name: Major Turr Phennir
Lore: 'Executive officer of the 181st Imperial Fighter Wing. Older brother killed by Wedge Antillies at the Battle of Yavin.',
Text: 'Adds 3 to power of any TIE he pilots. When piloting Saber 2, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. Once per game, you may take Fighters Coming In into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
